+# Pruned designs
+
+- Format registry / strategy / base `Exporter` class for csv/markdown:
+  rejected. Only JSON is required NOW; the discipline needs >=2 real variants
+  before abstracting. A plain `cmd_export` writing JSON is the minimal seam and
+  stays easy to extend later.
+- Adding an `export`/serialize helper to store.py: rejected. `store.load`
+  already returns the notes list; writing JSON is a one-liner in the CLI layer,
+  no store change needed.
