@@ -0,0 +1,13 @@
+# Corridor: E1-B-1-export-json
+
+Add an `export <outfile>` subcommand that writes all notes to `<outfile>`
+as a JSON array.
+
+Seam: `cli.py build_parser()` subparsers + a `cmd_export` handler that reuses
+`store.load(args.store)` (same source `cmd_list` reads). No store.py change —
+`load` already returns the list of notes.
+
+## Paths
+- cli_notes/cli.py
+- tests/test_cli.py
+- .slime/**
